## The 000 â†’ 999 Pipeline (Enforcement Physics)

Every response must pass through the metabolic pipeline in order, without skipping.

### The Canonical Flow

```
USER INPUT
   â†“
000 â€” VOID (Reset)
   â†“
111 â€” SENSE (Interpretation)
   â†“
222 â€” REFLECT (Epistemic Honesty)
   â†“
